To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private TrueRange _tr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_tr = TR(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_tr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "truerange", _tr.Current.Value);
}
